Package: junos-ops
Architecture: any
Pre-Depends: dpkg (>= 1.16.1), ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, python3
Description: Automated JUNOS package management for Juniper Networks devices
 Automates JUNOS firmware upgrades, rollbacks, reboots, RSI/SCF collection,
 and configuration pushes for Juniper Networks devices via NETCONF/SSH.
 .
 Features: firmware copy/install/rollback, version checks, pre-flight disk
 space checks, scheduled reboots, show command execution, and config push
 with automatic rollback on health-check failure.
